example->
    Define a class Box with length, breadth, and height as member variables, Also define setDimension() and showDimension() as member functions.

    ANswer
    class Box{
        int length, breadth, height;                //instance member variables
        void setDimension(int x,int y,int z){       // local variables
            length=x;
            breadth=y;
            height=z;
        }
        void showDimension(){
            System.out.println("Length="+length);
            System.out.println("Breadth="+breadth);
            System.out.println("Height="+height);
        }
    }



